Class V2LicenseApplicationContext

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class V2LicenseApplicationContext
extends TrueLicenseApplicationContext<V2RepositoryModel>
    The root context for applications which need to manage V2/* format license keys.

    This class is immutable.

      • pbeAlgorithm

        public final String pbeAlgorithm()
        Returns the name of the default Password Based Encryption (PBE) algorithm for the license key format. You can override this default value when configuring the PBE.

        The implementation in the class V2LicenseApplicationContext returns "PBEWithSHA1AndDESede".

        Specified by:

      • storeType

        public final String storeType()
        Returns the name of the default key store type, for example "JCEKS" or "JKS". You can override this default value when configuring the key store based authentication.

        The implementation in the class V2LicenseApplicationContext returns "JCEKS".
